-- Argentina Appoints Sergio Batista as National Soccer Coach Through 2014
-- B y   R o d r i g o   O r i h u e l a
-- 2010-11-02T23:51:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/argentina-appoints-sergio-batista-as-national-soccer-coach-through-2014.html
Argentina appointed Sergio Batista as
head coach of the national soccer team until the end of the 2014
World Cup, the Argentine Football Association said.  Batista, 47, had been caretaker coach since Diego Maradona
left the job on July 28.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rodrigo Orihuela in Buenos Aires at 
 rorihuela@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
